### 4. Mystery Guest — `ImportOrders_FromCsv_ParsesCorrectly` (line 144)

Hard-coded path `C:\TestData\orders.csv` is an invisible external dependency. The test will fail on any machine without that exact file at that exact path (every Linux CI agent, every teammate's Mac).

```csharp
