### 9. Assertion Roulette — `CalculateTotal_ReturnsCorrectAmount` (line 84)

Three assertions with no messages. When one fails, the test runner reports a line number but no description of *what was wrong*.

**Fix:** Add assertion messages:

```csharp
Assert.AreEqual(expected, order.TotalAmount, "Subtotal mismatch");
Assert.AreEqual(expectedTax, order.TaxAmount, "Tax mismatch");
Assert.AreEqual(expectedGrand, order.GrandTotal, "Grand total mismatch");
